title: "I Don't Have Time"
itunes:title: "I Don't Have Time"
description:
Episode 287 - This phrase is the biggest cop out in the world. Instead of saying “ I don’t have time” start saying “It’s just not a priority” because that is the truth. In this episode, I talk about how to set your priorities in order to do the things that you need to do to be successful.
